## 1. Service Overview

{{ service_name }} is responsible for {{ purpose | default(value="core platform functionality") }}.

### Architecture
- **Runtime**: {{ runtime | default(value="see deployment config") }}
- **Health endpoint**: `http://localhost:{{ port }}{{ health_path | default(value="/health") }}`
- **Data store**: {{ data_store | default(value="see config") }}
- **Log output**: {{ log_output | default(value="stdout / structured JSON") }}

### Dependencies
{% for dep in dependencies -%}
- **{{ dep.name }}** ({{ dep.type | default(value="internal") }}): {{ dep.description | default(value="") }}{% if dep.critical %} [CRITICAL]{% endif %}
{% endfor %}

